articles.contents:
About Me
My name is Amisha Jain. I am 16 years old. I am a
junior at Metea Valley High School. Some facts about me are I am a black
belt in karate and I love to read!
About the Project
Title: Fuel Efficiency and Weight
Description: My project, Fuel Efficiency and
Weight, involves a plot of how certain cars are different amounts
of fuel efficient.
Goals
Look at MPG of cars
The data might show inaccurate MPG

Look at weight of each car
“This is data science”

Preceptor

Kane’s Free High School
Data Science Bootcamp
